HEADWORD: Triclinic
<hw>Tri*clin"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>tri-</ets> + Gr. <?/ to incline.]</ety> <fld>(Crystallog.)</fld>
<def>Having, or characterized by, three unequal axes intersecting at
oblique angles. See the Note under <er>crystallization</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

